FIND : 

    FIND BY NAME IN DIRECTORY : find /Directory -type d -name Foldername

    FIND FILE OF X MB SIZE : find /Path/ -size XM

    FIND BY TYPE : find /Path/ -type f 

        FILE : f
        FOLDER : d
        SYMBOLIC LINK : l
        BLOCK DEVICE : b
        SOCKET : s

    SEARCH FOR SPECIFIC USER : find /Path/ -user UserName

    SEARCH FOR INODE NUMBER : find /Path/ -inum INODE_NUM

    SEARCH ON BASIS OF NUMBER OF LINKS : find /Path/ -links NUM

    SEARCH MATCHING PERMISSIONS : find /Path/ -oerm /u=rwx

    SEARCH EMPTY FILES ; find /Path/ -empty

    SEARCH FOR SIZE FROM X TO Y MB : find /Path/ -size +X -size -Y


FIND AND EXECUTE : 

    FIND AND DELETE EMPTY FILES : find . -empty -exec rm {} \;

